ğŸŒŸ 5ï¸âƒ£ Car Movement Script
Step 5.1 Create Script

Right click Project Window â†’ Create â†’ C# Script

Name: CarController

Paste this code:

using UnityEngine;

public class CarController : MonoBehaviour
{
    public float speed = 10f;
    public float turnSpeed = 50f;
    private Rigidbody rb;

    void Start()
    {
        rb = GetComponent<Rigidbody>();
    }

    void FixedUpdate()
    {
        float move = Input.GetAxis("Vertical") * speed;
        float turn = Input.GetAxis("Horizontal") * turnSpeed;

        rb.MovePosition(transform.position + transform.forward * move * Time.deltaTime);
        transform.Rotate(Vector3.up * turn * Time.deltaTime);
    }
}

Step 5.2 Attach Script

Drag CarController.cs onto Car

Run â†’ Car now moves with WASD / Arrow keys

ğŸŒŸ 6ï¸âƒ£ Create Collectible Points
