ğŸ‘‰ This is how script detects it.

ğŸŒŸ 7ï¸âƒ£ Create Score System
Step 7.1 UI

Right click Hierarchy â†’ UI â†’ Text - Legacy

Rename: ScoreText

Change text to: Score: 0

Step 7.2 Create Script

Right click Project â†’ Create â†’ C# Script

Name: PointSystem

Paste:

using UnityEngine;
using UnityEngine.UI;

public class PointSystem : MonoBehaviour
{
    public int score = 0;
    public Text scoreText;

    void OnTriggerEnter(Collider other)
    {
        if (other.CompareTag("Point"))
        {
            score++;
            scoreText.text = "Score: " + score;
            Destroy(other.gameObject);
        }
    }
}

Step 7.3 Attach to Car

Select Car

Add Component â†’ PointSystem

Drag ScoreText to script slot.

ğŸŒŸ 8ï¸âƒ£ Pause Menu System
Step 8.1 Create Canvas UI

Right click Hierarchy â†’ UI â†’ Canvas

Step 8.2 Create Pause Panel

Inside Canvas:

Right click â†’ UI â†’ Panel

Rename â†’ PausePanel

Set:

Active = OFF (disable)

Step 8.3 Create Buttons

Right click Panel â†’ UI â†’ Button

Text: Resume

Add another: Pause (outside panel)

Step 8.4 Create Pause Script

Create script: PauseMenu.cs

using UnityEngine;

public class PauseMenu : MonoBehaviour
{
    public GameObject pausePanel;

    public void PauseGame()
    {
        pausePanel.SetActive(true);
        Time.timeScale = 0;
    }

    public void ResumeGame()
    {
        pausePanel.SetActive(false);
        Time.timeScale = 1;
    }
}

Attach script:

Add to Canvas

Drag PausePanel â†’ Inspector â†’ pausePanel

Link buttons:

Pause â†’ OnClick â†’ Canvas â†’ PauseGame()

Resume â†’ OnClick â†’ Canvas â†’ ResumeGame()

ğŸŒŸ 9ï¸âƒ£ Mute/Unmute Audio
Step 9.1 Add Audio

Create empty object â†’ AudioManager

