Step 9.2 Script

Create script: AudioController.cs

using UnityEngine;

public class AudioController : MonoBehaviour
{
    public AudioSource bgMusic;

    public void ToggleSound()
    {
        bgMusic.mute = !bgMusic.mute;
    }
}


Attach to AudioManager
Drag AudioSource â†’ bgMusic slot

Add UI button

OnClick â†’ AudioManager â†’ ToggleSound()

